itemDescription: senior British women's air force leader

wikipedia_page.main: Air Commandant Dame Nancy Marion Salmon  (2 May 1906 – 9 October 1999), also known after 1962 by her married name, Dame Nancy Snagge, was a senior British women's air force officer. She was Director of the Women's Royal Air Force (WRAF) from 1950 to 1956.
